    <description><![CDATA[
### Alfen ACE Service Installer

This package installs the **Alfen ACE Service Installer** for Windows.
ACE Service Installer is used by installers/service engineers to **configure and troubleshoot Alfen EV charging stations on location** (NG platform).

#### Package behavior
- Downloads the official vendor MSI
- Installs silently using MSI (`/qn /norestart`)
- Validates the download with a SHA256 checksum (set in chocolateyinstall.ps1)

#### Notes
The software may require Alfen credentials and/or appropriate permissions depending on your environment and charger configuration.

Vendor page:
https://knowledge.alfen.com/space/IN/1627488257/Download+the+ACE+Service+Installer
